Quran Audio Player

The Quran Audio Player is a simple web application that allows users to listen to audio recitations of the Quran. Users can play, pause, and navigate through different surahs using the provided controls.

Features

Play and pause audio playback.
Navigate to the next or previous surah.
Display the name of the currently playing surah.
Usage
Clone or download the repository to your local machine.
Ensure you have a modern web browser installed (e.g., Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox).
Open the index.html file in your web browser.
Click the "Play Audio" button to start listening to the recitation of the first surah.
Use the "Next Surah" and "Previous Surah" buttons to navigate through different surahs.
Enjoy listening to the Quran audio recitations.

Technology Used
.HTML
.CSS
.JavaScript